arStrings.szText: "I've done as you asked. Take me to Captain Kharov."
My my, Kharov will certainly be pleased! You were exemplary!
Kharov commands from a place the Dregs call Temple of the Profane. Under his guidance, it has transformed into a wonder!
We'll reconvene there, where you will participate in the Blood Pilgrimage. If you are to reach Kharov, you'll have to partake!
I'll have to weave your tale into his! How exciting! See you there!
